{"tid":1295960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈反送中運動失焦","createTime":"2019-07-08T07:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:44:44.000Z","uid":153748,"like":9,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74dc9a905517902441fbef3713e4ef5054dc0a3e","tid":1295960,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"柒柒柒匿埋左一個星期都冇<br />\n已經成功令件事變成警民衝突<br />\n分化我地削弱力量<br />\n而家只有支持警察同反警察既聲音<br />\n跟住既遊行就係反紅媒反水貨客<br />\n雖然大家終於可以將對蝗既不滿盡情訴說<br />\n政府咁拖落去<br />\n逃犯條例 始終都係會恢復二讀<br />\n題外話<br />\n每一日追post<br />\n同屋企人爭論誰是誰非 <br />\n同佢地解釋又解釋過 拗又拗過<br />\n一日比一日無力<br />\n磨滅意志<br />\n<br />\n不過都想講句<br />\n呢一個月 辛苦曬各位記者"},{"pid":"023213f871e36c7756097529c0de2578e0fa3c69","tid":1295960,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cc8e1b1eb8d4158b05a5ce8882f6385d787334","tid":1295960,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e362dd153b805b2c5814e18d58fd267054a2c2f","tid":1295960,"uid":59297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:00:17.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 送中個問題已經唔算大<br />\n<br />\n就算送中撤回咗，我地都要繼續打落去"},{"pid":"915e026fc5cb2ada562c20f893011b4bc2caaafb","tid":1295960,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f213f74c7f4d8afbb13bd730863d5e1a36b0acf","tid":1295960,"uid":225887,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"失乜撚野焦<br />\n依家反送中係一個爆發點<br />\n衍生出警權問題今日已經成為有史以來<br />\n最嚴重既制度問題 權力大撚過法律呀屌你<br />\n唔屌黑警屌咩"},{"pid":"6de0ecf7ab37474c5b9dfb62d56d4f9a1bc16864","tid":1295960,"uid":153748,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8e362dd153b805b2c5814e18d58fd267054